# Dashboard

Next.js 14 · Zustand · WebSocket (live badge) · REST polling for audit tail.

## Panels

- **Flight Recorder** — `flight-recorder-panel.tsx` → `/api/v1/audit/tail`
- **Analytics** — `analytics-panel.tsx` → outcome/source/MITRE charts
- **Export Pack** — link to `/api/v1/audit/export/evidence`

## Verify UI changes

```powershell
cd apps\dashboard && npm run build
```

Dev: `scripts\start-dev.bat` serves dashboard on `:3000`.
